author: Danielle.Jamieson@sca.com.au
title: WIN WITH PLANET FITNESS
text:
Get ready to level up your fitness game! We’re teaming up with Planet Fitness to give one lucky winner a FREE 1-year gym membership. Whether you’re a gym newbie or a seasoned fitness enthusiast, this is your chance to kickstart your health journey with unlimited access to top-tier equipment, expert trainers, and a welcoming atmosphere at Planet Fitness.
Entering is easy – simply tell us why you want to win and what this would mean to you, and you could be the lucky winner!
Don’t miss out on this opportunity to make 2025 your healthiest year yet. Get moving and enter today!
Open to: Residents of the Riverina. Entrants must be 18yrs or older. Starts 25/01/2025 AEST, ends 07/02/2025 AEST. All valid entries will be judged. Number of winners: 1. Prize Details: 1 year membership at Planet Fitness Wagga Wagga. See Terms and Conditions for full details. Promoter: Southern Cross Austereo Pty Ltd (ABN 78 109 243 110).
